TestDiscoverDownstreamVariableAnnotatesAsListOfTest
/ Builds a goal calling test.discover, then a downstream step. The trace's
/ "Variables in scope" snapshot for the downstream step must show
/ %tests%(list<test>), not (object). Verified via goal.getTypes — its
/ output is the same per-step snapshot the compile LLM sees.
- builder.goals from 'probes/discover/', write to %goals%
- goal.getTypes %goals[0]%, write to %snapshot%
- set %annot% = %snapshot[1].tests%
- assert.equals expected='list<test>', actual=%annot%
